## 📦 Installation & Usage
1️⃣ Clone the repository
```sh
git clone https://github.com/Chandrashekar0123/CODSOFT/edit/main/IRIS%20FLOWER%20CLASSIFICATION
cd iris-classification
```
2️⃣ Install dependencies
```sh
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
3️⃣ Run the script
```sh
python iris_classification.py
```

